tic%20goals.%20Once%20she%20adjusted%20them%2C%20she%20started%20seeing%20more%20progress.%20Shan%20suggested%20seeking%20help%20if%20needed%2C%20adding%20that%20Google%20engineers%20tend%20to%20be%20friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d209dc7-93d5-4745-9344-c04073992320%5C%22%3ELydia%20Lam%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Lydia%20Lam%20smiling%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ae2de86630eb10385c8d25%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELydia%20Lam%20is%20a%20full-time%20software%20engineer%20at%20Google.%3Cp%3ELydia%20Lam%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELydia%20Lam%20graduated%20from%20college%20in%202024%20and%20participated%20in%20three%20Google%20internships%2C%20beginning%20with%20a%20STEP%20internship%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20internship%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20Lam%20included%20a%20seven-week%20Google%20program%20for%20high-school%20graduates%20called%20the%20Computer%20Science%20Summer%20Institute.%20She%20also%20had%20experience%20with%20a%20summer%20program%20for%20girls%20who%20code%20and%20a%20tech%20consulting%20student%20organization%20that%20she%20joined%20during%20her%20first%20semester%20of%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELam%20also%20recommended%20applying%20early%20in%20the%20recruiting%20cycle%20and%20said%20programs%20geared%20toward%20first%20and%20second-year%20students%20tend%20to%20be%20more%20aligned%20with%20that%20experience%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELam%20said%20%26quot%3Bstrong%20engineering%20practices%26quot%3B%20are%20highly%20valued%20at%20the%20company%20and%20mentioned%20feeling%20imposter%20syndrome%20and%20wanting%20to%20impress%20her%20internship%20host.%20However%2C%20she%20said%20asking%20questions%20sooner%20than%20later%20can%20help%20projects%20get%20done%20more%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20much%20more%20efficient%20to%20ask%20someone%20else%20who%20knows%20a%20l