sending%20texts%20to%20each%20other%20about%20what%20an%20asshole%20the%20other%20person%20is%2C%20not%20paying%20attention%2C%20not%20reading%20your%20stuff.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20firm's%20workers%20are%20already%20back%20in%20the%20office%20five%20days%20a%20week.%20JPMorgan%20has%20said%20in-person%20work%20is%20the%20best%20way%20to%20run%20the%20company%20and%20that%20the%20benefits%20of%20being%20together%20are%20%26quot%3Bsubstantial%20and%20irreplaceable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20didn't%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20additional%20comment%20on%20the%20motivation%20for%20the%20bank's%20tighter%20RTO%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c9f2a490-9e63-4dad-b3d7-d6ecede566db%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECrimping%20flexibility%20can%20hurt%20engagement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETempting%20as%20it%20might%20be%2C%20ratcheting%20up%20control%20over%20workers%20by%20removing%20flexibility%20often%20%26quot%3Bdrives%20down%20engagement%2C%26quot%3B%20Brian%20Elliott%2C%20a%20former%20executive%20at%20Slack%20who%20is%20now%20CEO%20of%20Work%20Forward%2C%20an%20advisory%20firm%20on%20future-of-work%20issues%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20get%20what%20you%20asked%20for%20if%20you're%20not%20careful%2C%20which%20is%20disengaged%20employees%20who%20are%20there%20to%20punch%20a%20clock%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20might%20already%20be%20happening.%20Gallup%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gallup.com%2F401384%2Findicator-hybrid-work.aspx%23ite-510899%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20late%202024%20found%20that%20workers%20who%20could%20do%20their%20jobs%20remotely%20but%20were%20on-site%20each%20workday%20showed%20the%20biggest%20drops%20in%20engagement%20since%202020.%20Both%20hybrid%20and%20fully%20remote%20workers%20reported%20higher%20levels%20of%20feeling%20connected%20to%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENicole%20Kyle%2C%20who%20researches%20the%20future%20of%20work%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20it's%20not%20accurate%20to%20assume%20that%20engagement%20levels%20are%20higher%20when%20workers%20are%20in%20the%20office.%20Yet%2C%20often%2C%20that's%20something%20leaders%20often%20gravitate%20toward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20RTO%20lever%20is%20the%20easy%20one%20to%20pull%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemote%20or%20hybrid%20arrangements%20can%20give%20workers%20a%20stronger%20sense%20of%20autonomy%2C%20said%20Kyle%2C%20who%20is%20cofounder%20of%20CMP%20Research.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20is%20less%20engaging%20to%20employees%20than%20not%20having%20flexibility%20and%20choice%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2243d16f77-25f6-4d86-a249-61f576ba91b4%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Predictable%20flexibility'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGinnie%20Carlier%2C%20Americas%20vice%20chair%20for%20talent%20at%20EY%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20firm's%20employees%20tend%20to%20work%20with%20their%20team%20leaders%20to%20plan%20days%20in%20the%20office%20%E2%80%94%20an%20approach%20she%20refers%20to%20as%20%26quot%3Bpredictable%20flexibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20one%20that's%20proven%20fruitful%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20most%20engaged%20and%20highest-performing%20individuals%20are%20the%20ones%20that%20are%20on%20a%20hybrid%20work%20arrangement%2C%26quot%3B%20Carlier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20EY%20workers%2C%20that%20means%20spending%20two%20to%20three%20days%20a%20week%20in%20the%20office%2C%20she%20said.%20The%20focus%20is%20on%20how%20teams%20can%20work%20best%20together%2C%20not%20solely%20on%20how%20much%20gets%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20really%20gotten%20away%20from%20this%20discussion%20around%20this%20illusion%20of%20increased%20productivity%20by%20being%20in%20the%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20Carlier%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20when%20EY%20surveys%20new%20hires%20about%20why%20they%20accepted%20a%20job%20with%20the%20firm%2C%20flexibility%20reliably%20is%20one%20of%20the%20top%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStudies%20from%20numerous%20settings%20show%20that%20giving%20people%20flexibility%20in%20how%20they%20work%20%E2%80%94%20and%20allowing%20them%20to%20work%20remotely%20part%20of%20the%20time%20%E2%80%94%20raises%20productivity%2C%20retention%2C%20worker%20satisfaction%2C%20and%20engagement%2C%20Siri%20Chilazi%2C%20a%20senior%20researcher%20at%20the%20Women%20and%20Public%20Policy%20Program%20at%20Harvard's%20Kennedy%20School%20of%20Government%20and%20the%20coauthor%20of%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BMake%20Work%20Fair%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f5b9135-186a-4ca5-98f9-5173003b036e%5C%22%3EFlexibility%20can%20also%20bring%20challenges%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJohn%20Rossman%2C%20a%20business%20strategist%20who%20was%20an%20early%20exec%20at%20Amazon%20and%20is%20the%20author%20of%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BThe%20Amazon%20Way%2C%26quot%3B%20told%20BI%20that%20it%20can%20be%20easier%20for%20workers%20to%20be%20disengaged%20when%20they%20don't%20face%20the%20%26quot%3Bpeer%20pressure%26quot%3B%20of%20being%20observed%20by%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20trying%20to%20increase%20engagement%20shouldn't%20be%20the%20main%20reason%20employers%20require%20workers%20to%20be%20in%20the%20office%2C%20though%20he%20said%20the%20move%20could%20reveal%20which%20workers%20feel%20most%20connected%20to%20their%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20people%20who%20really%20want%20to%20be%20there%20are%20going%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Rossman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20way%20to%20boost%20worker%20engagement%20is%20through%20training%2C%20Joe%20Galvin%2C%20chief%20research%20officer%20at%20the%20executive-coaching%20firm%20Vistage%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20helping%20workers%20build%20their%20skills%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0especially%20in%20an%20environment%20where%20technology%20like%20artificial%20intelligence%20promises%20to%20reshape%20many%20jobs%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0can%20result%20in%20employers%20having%20more%20%26quot%3Bhighly%20engaged%20A%20players.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20do%20it%20as%20best%20they%20can.%20They're%20focused%20on%20quantity.%20They%20focus%20on%20quality.%20They%20do%20all%20the%20right%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Galvin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frto-office-full-time-could-hurt-worker-engagement-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739787721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67afbf757bb3f854015d04f8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frto-office-full-time-could-hurt-worker-engagement-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Worker%20engagement%20in%20the%20US%20is%20at%20its%20lowest%20level%20in%20a%20decade.%20Full-time%20return-to-office%20mandates%20could%20worsen%20the%20situation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tparadis%40businessinsider.com%20(Tim%20Paradis)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frto-office-full-time-could-hurt-worker-engagement-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Video%20of%20RPF%20constable%20carrying%20her%20child%20at%20NDLS%20is%20winning%20hearts%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739787550000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118327853%2Cimgsize-615676.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Flife-style%2Fparenting%2Fmoments%2Fvideo-of-mom-carrying-her-child-and-performing-duties-at-new-delhi-railway-station-is-winning-hearts%2Farticleshow%2F118327812.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20viral%20video%20from%20New%20Delhi%20Railway%20Station%20shows%20a%20determined%20mother%20and%20RPF%20officer%20maintaining%20order%20wi