%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Ftehran-blasts-netanyahu-vow-to-finish-the-job-against-iran%2Famp_articleshow%2F118326261.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'No%20demolition%20until%20further%20order'%3A%20SC%20to%20UP%20govt%20over%20Kushinagar%20mosque%20razing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739783421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118326120%2Cimgsize-68636.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fno-demolition-until-further-order-supreme-court-notice-to-up-govt-over-demolition-at-kushinagar-mosque%2Farticleshow%2F118326149.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20authorities%20over%20a%20contempt%20petition%20alleging%20unauthorized%20demolition%20of%20parts%20of%20Madni%20Masjid%20in%20Kushinagar%2C%20violating%20a%20prior%20order.%20Petitioners%20claim%20the%20February%202025%20demolition%20occurred%20without%20prior%20notice%20or%20hearing%2C%20and%20seek%20restoration%20or%20compensation%20for%20the%20damaged%20structure.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20helped%20my%20mom%20set%20up%20her%20phone.%20It%20could%20have%20gone%20better.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20elderly%20woman%20with%20different%20kinds%20of%20app%20floating%20around%20her%20head.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67afa984eb4be2fff9a4c12e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDUMMY%20IMAGE%20FOR%20OLD%20PEOPLE%20TECH%3Cp%3EAlex%20Castro%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20stepfather%20died%20a%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20after%20a%20long%20decade%20dealing%20with%20Parkinson's%20disease.%20Doug%20was%20living%20in%20a%20care%20facility%2C%20and%20even%20though%20my%20mom%20visited%20all%20the%20time%2C%20for%20overall%20contact%20with%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20and%20just%20general%20fun%20%E2%80%94%20he%20relied%20on%20his%20phone%20and%20his%20iPad.%20But%20Parkinson's%20is%20a%20neuromuscular%20disorder%3B%20eventually%2C%20Doug's%20hands%20and%20fingers%20couldn't%20reliably%20navigate%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-is-working-on-touch-screen-macbook-pro-report-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etouchscreen%20or%20a%20keyboard%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20his%20dementia%20worsened%2C%20he%20couldn't%20really%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20buy%20stuff%20online%20anymore%2C%20much%20less%20how%20to%20manage%20a%20healthcare%20or%20banking%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20buying%20sketchy%20apps%20%E2%80%94%20probably%20without%20even%20realizing%20it%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sending%20disjointed%2C%20sometimes%20inappropriate%20emails%20and%20texts.%20We%20got%20worried%20he%20was%20going%20to%20do%20something%20bad%20with%20his%20bank%20accounts%2C%20or%20fall%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fphishing-scams-in-your-inbox-waiting-to-steal-your-money-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ephishing%20attack%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Apple's%20operating%20system%20has%20a%20tool%20that%20lets%20you%20limit%20which%20apps%20a%20user%20can%20access%3B%20my%20mom%20pared%20Doug's%20down%20to%20nearly%20nothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20thing%20is%2C%20Doug%20had%20been%20an%20IT%20guy.%20He%20loved%20computers.%20At%20work%2C%20he%20installed%20enterprise%20servers%20and%20helped%20maintain%20a%20citywide%20network.%20In%20his%20spare%20time%20he%20tinkered%20on%20a%20boat%20and%20built%20cabinets%3B%20he%20knew%20how%20to%20tie%20complicated%20knots.%20Doug%20had%2C%20I%20am%20saying%2C%20a%20technical%20mind.%20Right%20until%20the%20end%2C%20he%20%3Cem%3Ewanted%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20FaceTime%20my%20mom%2C%20email%20his%20medical%20team%2C%20and%20buy%20stuff%20from%20West%20Marine.%20He%20just%20wasn't%20able%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20older%20doesn't%20necessarily%20come%20with%20the%20kind%20of%20extreme%20disability%20Doug%20dealt%20with.%20But%20it%20inevitably%20brings%20to%20us%20all%20a%20bit%20of%20mental%20inflexibility%20and%20physical%20limitation.%20The%20ubiquitous%20gadgets%20and%20apps%20that%20are%20our%20windows%20onto%20the%20world%20aren't%20made%20for%20any%20of%20that%20%E2%80%94%20they're%20confusing%2C%20hard%20to%20use%2C%20ever-changing%2C%20and%20either%20too%20poorly%20or%20too%20well%20secured.%20And%20meanwhile%2C%20every%20sector%20of%20society%20is%20scrambling%20to%20trade%20storefronts%20for%20websites%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchatgpt-ai-will-not-take-jobs-create-future-work-opportunities-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ehuman%20staff%20for%20AI%20chatbots%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmericans%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faging-demographics-impact-on-economy-growth-markets-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eoldest%20we've%20ever%20been%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Many%20millennials%20are%20already%20old%20enough%20to%20need%20their%20phone%20flashlights%20to%20read%20the%20menu%20in%20a%20dimly%20lit%20restaurant%2C%20and%20the%20over-65%20population%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20from%2060%20million%20today%20to%2082%20million%20by%202050.%20Technology%20is%20designed%20by%2C%20and%20for%2C%20the%20young.%20So%20what%20happens%20when%20an%20unprecedented%20number%20of%20us%20are%20old%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EDebaleena%20Chattopadhyay%20is%20a%20primary%20caregiver%20for%20her%20parents%20%E2%80%94%20her%20mom%20is%2066%2C%20her%20dad%20is%2073.%20That's%20complicated%2C%20because%20Chattopadhyay%20is%20in%20Chicago%20and%20they%20live%20in%20India%2C%20where%20smartphone%20apps%20mediate%20just%20about%20every%20activity%20of%20daily%20life%2C%20from%20finances%20to%20healthcare%20to%20food%20delivery.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20dad%20was%20still%20working%2C%20computerized%20banking%20was%20introduced%2C%20and%20he%20was%20very%20proud.%20He%20helped%20everyone%2C%26quot%3B%20Chattopadhyay%20says.%20%26quot%3BNow%20he%20can't%20do%20anything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20strong%20dad%20energy%20will%20always%20prevail.%20The%20other%20day%2C%20Chattopadhyay%20tells%20me%2C%20a%20restaurant's%20online%20order%20form%20so%20confused%20her%20dad%20that%20he%20just%20telephoned%20instead.%20But%20the%20guy%20on%20the%20phone%20told%20him%20he'd%20get%20a%20discount%20if%20he%20used%20the%20app.%20So%20her%20dad%20hung%20up%2C%20dragged%20himself%20to%20the%20restaurant%2C%20and%20had%20the%20guy%20who'd%20answered%20his%20call%20use%20the%20app%20to%20put%20in%20his%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChattopadhyay%20says%20that%20kind%20of%20technological%20madness%20is%20coming%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20And%20she%20would%20know%20%E2%80%94%20she's%20a%20researcher%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Illinois%20Chicago%20who%20studies%20how%20older%20adults%20interact%20with%20computers.%20It's%20a%20wide-open%20field%2C%20because%20the%20research%20from%20just%20a%20couple%20of%20decades%20back%20got%20a%20whole%20bunch%20of%20things%20terribly%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20early%20days%20of%20mobile%20phones%20and%20MP3s%2C%20researchers%20assumed%20that%20older%20people%20would%20be%20resistant%20to%20digital%20technology%20in%20any%20form%20%E2%80%94%20preferring%2C%20presumably%2C%20to%20shout%20at%20clouds%20or%20watch%20television%20with%20the%20volume%20turned%20way%20up.%20So%20the%20focus%20turned%20to%20developing%20tech%20meant%20to%20help%20old%20people%20with%20old-people%20things%2C%20like%20reminders%20to%20take%20their%20medications%20or%20games%20to%20aid%20their%20memory.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EResearchers%20also%20worked%20on%20creating%20elderized%20versions%20of%20familiar%20products%2C%20like%20phones%20with%20giant%20buttons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEveryone%20hated%20that%20stuff.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I%20tell%20you%2C%20'You're%20old%2C%20you%20should%20use%20Facebook%20for%20Seniors%2C'%20that's%20infantilizing%2C%26quot%3B%20Chattopadhyay%20says.%20Older%20people%20want%20to%20do%20the%20same%20kinds%20of%20things%20with%20computers%20as%20anyone%20else%20%E2%80%94%20edit%20videos%2C%20talk%20to%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20share%20Spotify%20playlists%2C%20call%20an%20Uber%2C%20whatever.%20And%20they%20want%20to%20use%20the%20same%2C%20or%20similar%2C%20tools%20everyone%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20also%20true%20that%20with%20age%2C%20our%20eyesight%20and%20hearing%20get%20worse.%20Texting%20thumbs%20get%20arthritic.%20Memory%20gets%20slippery.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAnd%20maybe%20most%20significantly%2C%20age%20can%20reduce%20what%20researchers%20call%20%26quot%3Bfluid%20intelligence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20cognitive%20flexibility%20that%20enables%20us%20to%20multitask%20and%20learn%20new%20things%20%E2%80%94%20like%20where%20the%20hell%20the%20damn%20search%20button%20went%20in%20the%20latest%20app%20update.%20Plus%2C%20older%20people%20kind%20of%20stop%20wanting%20to%20bother.%20How%20many%20versions%20of%20Word%20do%20you%20have%20to%20live%20through%20before%20deciding%2C%20eh%2C%20maybe%20I%20don't%20need%20the%20new%20one%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20core%20problem%20that%20even%20sophisticated%20digital%20natives%20face%20as%20they%20age.%20Innovative%20features%2C%20updated%20apps%2C%20and%20entirely%20new%20products%20are%20how%20tech%20companies%20grow%20and%20make%20money.%20They're%20also%20exactly%20what%20older%20adults%20have%20trouble%20metabolizing.%20So%20the%20more%20exciting%20ways%20a%20tech%20company%20finds%20to%20step%20boldly%20into%20the%20future%2C%20the%20more%20users%20get%20stuck%20in%20the%20past.%20%26quot%3BOlder%20adults%20will%20say%2C%20'I%20have%20been%20working%20with%20computers%20since%20the%201980s%2C%20and%20now%20the%20Calendar%20app%20has%20changed%2C%20and%20I%20can't%20use%20it%2C'%26quot%3B%20Chattopadhyay%20says.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20assume%20that%20if%20you%20grew%20up%20with%20AOL%2C%20you%20will%20be%20good%20with%20Gemini.%20But%20it's%20not%20the%20same.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ETech%20companies%20know%20what%20they're%20facing%20here.%20Apple%2C%20Google%2C%20and%20Microsoft%20offer%20all%20sorts%20of%20%26quot%3Baccommodations%26quot%3B%20to%20users%20%E2%80%94%20from%20text-to-speech%20and%20live%20captioning%20to%20audible%20alarms.%20Last%20year%2C%20Google%20finished%20an%20international%20research%20program%20on%20older%20users'%20needs%2C%20finding%20that%20they%20wanted%20tech%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bempowering%2C%20clear%2C%20and%20intuitive%2C%20but%20not%20overly%20reduced%20or%20overly%20simplified%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Laura%20Allen%2C%20the%20company's%20director%20of%20accessibility%20and%20disability%20inclusion.%20In%20response%2C%20Google%20introduced%20something%20called%20Simple%20View%20for%20its%20phone%20software.%20Activated%20on%20setup%2C%20it%20not%20only%20increases%20font%20and%20app%20sizes%20but%20also%20adds%20a%20home%20button%2C%20a%20go-back%20button%2C%20and%20a%20recent-app%20button.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAllen%20understands%20the%20value%20of%20these%20kinds%20of%20assistive%20technologies%20%E2%80%94%20she%20relies%20on%20them%20to%20help%20with%20her%20own%20vision%20impairment.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20out%20at%20multiple%20dinners%20with%20my%20parents%2C%20who%20have%20been%20losing%20just%20slight%20visual%20acuity%20over%20the%20years%2C%20and%20none%20of%20us%20could%20see%20the%20menu%2C%26quot%3B%20Allen%20says.%20%26quot%3BI%20pass%20around%20my%20Pixel%20with%20the%20Magnifier%20app%20open%2C%20and%20they're%20like%2C%20'Oh%2C%20my%20gosh%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20amazing!'%20These%20kinds%20of%20apps%20are%20just%20universally%20useful%2C%20and%20my%20parents%20had%20no%20idea%20they%20were%20available.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20kinds%20of%20tech%20that%20help%20people%20with%20physical%20issues%20like%20vision%20or%20hearing%20impairments%20aren't%20what%20some%20older%20users%20are%20looking%20for.%20One%20recent%20journal%20article%20warned%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fdx.doi.org%2F10.1145%2F3431280%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eharm%20in%20conflating%20aging%20with%20accessibility%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20That's%20to%20say%2C%20functions%20that%20make%20screens%20easier%20to%20read%20and%20phones%20easier%20to%20use%20are%20important%2C%20but%20they%20miss%20the%20point.%20The%20tech%20industry%20is%20mostly%20young%2C%20fit%2C%20busy%20gadgeteers%20building%20products%20for%20younger%2C%20fitter%2C%20busier%20users.%20Anything%20outside%20that%20category%20is%20viewed%20as%20a%20disability%20they%20grudgingly%20accommodate.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%3A%20How%20can%20we%20develop%20technology%20for%20things%20that%20older%20adults%20would%20want%3F%26quot%3B%20says%20Karyn%20Moffatt%2C%20a%20researcher%20in%20human-computer%20interaction%20at%20McGill%20University.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20mobile%20banking.%20It's%20life-changingly%20convenient%20to%20be%20able%20to%20transfer%20funds%20and%20make%20deposits%20on%20your%20phone%2C%20but%20our%20financial%20well-being%20now%20depends%20in%20no%20small%20part%20on%20our%20ability%20to%20thumb-type%20accurately%20and%20remember%20long%20strings%20of%20alphanumeric%20nonsense.%20%26quot%3BMobile%20banking%2C%20we're%20assuming%20a%20lot%20of%20responsibility%20for%20errors%2C%26quot%3B%20Moffatt%20says.%20Lots%20of%20older%20folks%20rely%20on%20friends%2C%20relatives%2C%20or%20caregivers%20as%20informal%20banking%20helpers%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20can%20require%20risky%20moves%20like%20sharing%20passwords.%20So%20a%20research%20team%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Manitoba%20is%20looking%20at%20approaches%20that%20would%20let%20older%20adults%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1145%2F3670947.3670962%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Edelegate%20a%20proxy%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20limited%2C%20flexible%20access%20to%20do%20things%20like%20pay%20only%20certain%20bills%2C%20or%20move%20money%20around%20with%20case-by-case%20approval.%20That%20preserves%20the%20older%20customer's%20independence%2C%20while%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20caregivers%20to%20provide%20a%20much-needed%20backstop.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20set%20up%20a%20bank%20account%20for%20my%20daughter%2C%20and%20because%20she's%20a%20minor%2C%20I%20can%20have%20access%2C%26quot%3B%20Moffatt%20says.%20But%20for%20older%20adults%2C%20the%20options%20are%20thin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20hand%20reaches%20toward%20a%20watch%20with%20a%20digital%20screen%20worn%20on%20the%20person's%20wrist%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ad0cf56630eb10385c72a6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOlder%20adults%20love%20tech%20as%20much%20as%20anyone%2C%20but%20the%20learning%20curve%20on%20new%20gadgets%20is%20steep.%3Cp%3EGenaro%20Molina%2FLos%20Angeles%20Times%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOr%20take%20exercise.%20Researchers%20used%20to%20think%20that%20older%20people%20didn't%20want%20to%20work%20out%2C%20and%20that%20a%20gadget%20like%20a%20Fitbit%20or%20some%20other%20gamified%20nudge-reminder%20tech%20would%20get%20them%20off%20the%20couch.%20But%20it%20turns%20out%20older%20folks%20were%20actually%20being%20prevented%20from%20getting%20off%20the%20couch%20by%20simple%20things%20like%20an%20absent%20workout%20buddy%20or%20inclement%20weather.%20Moffatt%20imagines%20that%20a%20workout%20gadget%20could%20use%20shared%20calendars%2C%20weather%20reports%2C%20and%20other%20relevant%20info%20to%20help%20aging%20jocks%20better%20navigate%20their%20infirmities%20and%20stick%20to%20their%20workout%20routines.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20something%20as%20basic%20as%20instruction%20manuals%20could%20stand%20improvement.%20Older%20users%20love%20tech%20as%20much%20as%20anyone%2C%20but%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20slower%20in%20absorbing%20how%20to%20use%20new%20gear%2C%20and%20more%20worried%20they're%20going%20to%20break%20it.%20A%20persistent%2C%20always-on%20chatbot%20could%20serve%20as%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdoi.org%2F10.1145%2F3411764.3445702%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eenhanced%20user%20manual%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20standing%20by%20to%20answer%20baffled%20questions%20like%20%26quot%3BWhere's%20the%20'like'%20button%3F%26quot%3B%20Or%20online%20manuals%20could%20offer%20older%20users%20a%20virtual%20sandbox%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20try%20out%20various%20settings%20before%20turning%20them%20on%20for%20real.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20so%20much%20potential%20for%20technology%20to%20facilitate%20things%20as%20we%20get%20older%2C%20to%20provide%20real%20services%20that%20are%20valuable%20and%20meaningful%2C%26quot%3B%20Moffatt%20says.%20%26quot%3BBut%20for%20the%20most%20part%2C%20we're%20not%20building%20those%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20mom's%20healthy%2C%20but%20she's%20in%20her%2080s%2C%20and%20I%20live%20hundreds%20of%20miles%20away.%20She%20has%20friendly%20neighbors%2C%20but%20if%20she%20fell%2C%20it%20could%20be%20hours%20before%20anyone%20figured%20it%20out.%20So%20she%20recently%20bought%20an%20Apple%20Watch%2C%20which%20provides%20shareable%20location%20tracking%20and%20fall%20monitoring.%20(The%20truth%20is%2C%20Mom%20likes%20cool%20gadgets%2C%20and%20she'd%20been%20wanting%20to%20replace%20her%20Garmin%20fitness%20watch%20anyway.%20Plus%2C%20she%20found%20the%20idea%20of%20paying%20for%20stuff%20and%20listening%20to%20audiobooks%20with%20her%20watch%20kind%20of%20magical.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20itching%20to%20have%20surveillance%20data%20on%20my%20mom.%20But%20I%20didn't%20know%20what%20else%20to%20do.%20So%2C%20during%20an%20epic%20session%20over%20Thanksgiving%2C%20we%20figured%20out%20how%20to%20make%20my%20phone%20sync%20with%20her%20watch's%20location.%20While%20we%20were%20at%20it%2C%20she%20also%20insisted%20that%20I%20set%20up%20a%20bunch%20of%20shared%20passwords%20and%20other%20information%20so%20I%20could%20get%20access%20to%20things%20like%20her%20bank%20accounts%20and%20medical%20data%20%E2%80%94%20something%20she%20wished%20had%20been%20easier%20to%20do%20during%20Doug's%20long%20decline.%20We%20also%20reorganized%20the%20apps%20on%20her%20phone%20into%20folders%20she%20named%2C%20and%20I%20showed%20her%20some%20search%20tricks.%20It%20was%2C%20I'll%20admit%2C%20a%20little%20frustrating%20for%20both%20of%20us.%20I%20went%20too%20fast%3B%20she%20was%20worried%20she'd%20somehow%20mess%20up%20the%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMom%20uses%20an%20iPad%2C%20and%20I%20noticed%20that%20she%20was%20having%20to%20reach%20across%20the%20keyboard%20with%20her%20right%20hand%20to%20trigger%20the%20fingerprint%20ID.%20I%20told%20her%20she%20should%20add%20her%20left%20index%20finger%20to%20the%20security%20settings.%20Turned%20out%20she%20hadn't%20known%20that%20was%20even%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20showed%20her%20where%20to%20set%20it%20up%2C%20the%20on-screen%20instructions%20weren't%20very%20clear%20about%20where%20to%20put%20your%20finger%2C%20or%20how%20long%20to%20hold%20it%20there%2C%20or%20when%20to%20move%20it.%20Mom%20kept%20moving%20off%20the%20scanner%20too%20soon%2C%20and%20she'd%20have%20to%20start%20over.%20Finally%2C%20I%20took%20her%20hand%20and%20helped%20her%20hold%20her%20finger%20on%20the%20button.%20It%20wasn't%20the%20most%20comfortable%20way%20for%20us%20to%20face%20the%20future%2C%20honestly.%20But%20we%20didn't%20really%20have%20a%20choice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Fadam-rogers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EAdam%20Rogers%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-people-struggling-new-technology-aging-parents-kids-assistance-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739783281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67afaafbeb4be2fff9a4c1a8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-people-struggling-new-technology-aging-parents-kids-assistance-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tech%20gadgets%20could%20help%20us%20navigate%20our%20golden%20years.%20Instead%2C%20they're%20making%20things%20worse.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22arogers%40businessinsider.com%20(Adam%20Rogers)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Folder-people-struggling-new-technology-aging-parents-kids-assistance-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PM%20Modi's%20adviser%20calls%20USAID%20a%20'scam'%2C%20questions%20funding%20for%20India%20polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739783259000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fpm-modi-adviser-sanjeev-sanyal-doge-elon-musk-usaid-funds-india-elections-125021700415_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sanjeev%20Sanyal%20has%20questioned%20the%20recipients%20of%20the%20alleged%20US%20funds%20in%20India.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20he%20criticised%20USAID%2C%20demanding%20transparency%20regarding%20the%20funds%20allocated%20to%20India%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Fpm-modi-adviser-sanjeev-sanyal-doge-elon-musk-usaid-funds-india-elections-125021700415_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Leader's%20%26quot%3BChina%20Not%20Our%20Enemy%26quot%3B%20Remark%20Sparks%20Huge%20Row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ECongress%20veteran%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsam-pitroda-says-it-is-time-for-india-needs-to-stop-assuming-china-is-enemy-threat-blown-out-of-proportion-7728565%5C%22%3ESam%20Pitroda%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20party's%20overseas%20unit%2C%20has%20courted%20a%20new%20controversy%20after%20claiming%20that%20the%20threat%20from%20China%20is%20often%20blown%20out%20of%20proportion.%20His%20suggestion%20that%20India%20needs%20to%20stop%20considering%20the%20neighbouring%20country%20as%20an%20enemy%20drew%20a%20sharp%20backlash%20with%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20saying%20he%20has%20revealed%20an%20%26quot%3Bagreement%26quot%3B%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20by%20Mr%20Pitroda%2C%20who%20is%20not%20unknown%20to%20controversies%2C%20follow%20his%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi's%20assertion%20in%20the%20parliament%20that%20India%20had%20lost%20a%20part%20of%20its%20territory%20to%20China%2C%20a%20claim%20that%20has%20been%20trashed%20by%20the%20government.%20Speaking%20to%20IANS%2C%20the%20Congress%20leader%20claimed%20that%20India's%20approach%20to%20China%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bconfrontational%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20mindset%20needed%20to%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fsam-pitroda-news-people-in-east-look-chinese-south-like-africa-sam-pitroda-triggers-row-5615438%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BSouth%20Indians%20Look%20Like%20Africans...%26quot%3B%3A%20Sam%20Pitroda%20Embarrasses%20Congress%20Again%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20understand%20the%20threat%20from%20China.%20I%20think%20this%20issue%20is%20often%20blown%20out%20of%20proportion%20because%20the%20U.S.%20has%20a%20tendency%20to%20define%20an%20enemy.%20I%20believe%20the%20time%20has%20come%20for%20all%20nations%20to%20collaborate%2C%20not%20confront.%20Our%20approach%20has%20been%20confrontational%20from%20the%20very%20beginning%2C%20and%20this%20attitude%20creates%20enemies%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20garners%20support%20within%20the%20country.%20We%20need%20to%20change%20this%20mindset%20and%20stop%20assuming%20that%20China%20is%20the%20enemy%20from%20day%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20the%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reply%20came%20to%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20would%20be%20able%20to%20control%20the%20threats%20from%20China.%20India%20had%20rejected%20Trump's%20offer%20last%20month%20to%20mediate%20an%20end%20to%20border%20disputes%20with%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Obsession%20With%20China'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHitting%20back%20at%20Mr%20Pitroda%2C%20the%20BJP%20called%20his%20remarks%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20deep%20blow%20to%20India's%20identity%2C%20diplomacy%20and%20sovereignty%26quot%3B.%20These%20are%20not%20isolated%20statements%2C%20argued%20the%20BJP's%20Sudhanshu%20Trivedi%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20had%20made%20similar%20remarks%20in%20the%20past.%20Condemning%20the%20remarks%2C%20he%20called%20those%20an%20insult%20to%20the%20Indian%20soldiers%20killed%20in%20action%20during%20the%202020%20clashes%20in%20Galwan%20Valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%C2%A0ational%20spokesperson%20Tuhin%20Sinha%20said%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20Congress's%20obsession%20with%20China%20lies%20in%20a%202008%20Memorandum%20for%20Understanding%20(MoU)%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Chinese%20Communist%20Party%20(CCP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20who%20ceded%20away%2040%2C000%20square%20km%20of%20our%20land%20to%20China%2C%20still%20see%20no%20threat%20from%20the%20Dragon.%20No%20wonder%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20is%20in%20awe%20of%20China%20and%20was%20rooting%20for%20BRI%20one%20day%20before%20the%20IMEEC%20was%20announced.%20The%20crux%20of%20Congress%20party's%20obsessive%20fascination%20for%20China%2C%20lies%20hidden%20in%20the%20mysterious%202008%20Cong-CCP%20MOU%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Sinha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcouldve-chosen-better-words-sam-pitroda-after-congress-reappointment-5984529%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BCould've%20Chosen%20Better%20Words%26quot%3B%3A%20Sam%20Pitroda%20After%20Congress%20Reappointment%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MoU%20flagged%20by%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsecret%20deal%26quot%3B%20in%20an%20RTI%20response%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20in%202020%2C%20between%20the%20Indian%20Congress%20party%20and%20the%20CCP.%20It%20was%20signed%20on%20August%207%2C%202008%20to%20exchange%20%26quot%3Bhigh-level%20information%20and%20cooperation%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20foreign%20ministry's%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPradeep%20Bhandari%2C%20another%20BJP%20spokesperson%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20Mr%20Pitroda%20is%20a%20close%20aide%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20accused%20the%20Congress%20of%20prioritising%20China's%20interest%20above%20India's.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi's%20right-hand%20man%20Sam%20Pitroda%3A%20'China%20isn't%20our%20enemy'!%20This%20man%20sings%20endless%20praises%20of%20China%20while%20Congress%20party's%20signing%20of%20MoU%20in%202008%20reveal%20a%20cozy%20betrayal%20of%20India's%20interests%20and%20prioritising%20China's!%20It's%20crazy%20how%20Congress%20always%20manages%20to%20keep%20China%20and%20Pakistan's%20interests%20above%20ours%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRahul%20Gandhi's%20remote%20control%20is%20in%20the%20hand%20of%20George%20Soros%20and%20China%2C%26quot%3B%20alleged%20Mr%20Bhandari%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20billionaire%20philanthropist%20accused%20of%20trying%20to%20influence%20global%20politics%20through%20his%20Open%20Society%20Foundation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERead%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fs-jaishankar-explains-how-sam-pirodas-remarks-stem-from-a-colonial-mindset-5631036%5C%22%3ES%20Jaishankar%20Says%20Sam%20Pitroda's%20Remarks%20Stem%20From%20A%20'Colonial%20Mindset'%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20been%20among%20the%20US'%20major%20headaches%20in%20view%20of%20security%20concerns%20and%20trade%20implications.%20India%20too%20has%20been%20engaged%20in%20a%20border%20dispute%20with%20China%2C%20which%20was%20marked%20by%20violent%20clashes%20in%202020.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20a%20disengagement%20process%20and%20military-level%20talks%20between%20the%20two%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20in%20India%20claims%20the%20country%20had%20lost%20a%20chunk%20of%20its%20land%20to%20China%20during%20these%20clashes%20-%20a%20claim%20that%20resurfaced%20in%20Mr%20Gandhi's%20parliament%20speech%20earlier%20this%20month.%20Mr%20Gandhi%20had%20claimed%20China%20has%20control%20over%204%2C000%20sq%20km%20of%20Indian%20territory%2C%20which%20was%20refuted%20by%20Defence%20Minister%20Rajnath%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESam%20Pitroda's%20Controversies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Pitroda%20has%20courted%20controversies%20in%20the%20past%20well.%20His%20comments%20in%202024%20on%20the%20diversity%20among%20Indians%20were%20seen%20as%20racist%20and%20even%20drew%20backlash%20from%20PM%20Modi.%20He%2C%20however%2C%20had%20stood%20by%20his%20remarks%20and%20blamed%20it%20on%20the%20words%20that%20he%20chose%20to%20express%20himself.%20The%20Congress%20had%20distanced%20itself%20from%20his%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20an%20uproar%2C%20he%20had%20given%20up%20his