the%20simultaneous%20sale%20of%20around%201%2C500%20general%20category%20tickets%2C%20exacerbated%20the%20situation%20and%20contributed%20to%20the%20overcrowding%20of%20platforms%2013%20and%2014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20date%20of%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20is%20February%2026.%20This%20means%20lakhs%20of%20devotees%20are%20still%20trying%20to%20reach%20the%20holy%20city%20to%20immerse%20themselves%20in%20the%20'%3Cem%3Esangam%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20or%20the%20confluence%20of%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20prevent%20another%20Kumbh-related%20tragedy%2C%20colour-coded%20enclosures%2C%20'enhanced%20tech'%20to%20monitor%20crowds%2C%20and%20crisis-management%20training%20to%20railway%20officials%20will%20be%20part%20of%20a%20six-month%20campaign%20that%20will%20also%20see%20Delhi's%20stations%20will%20undergo%20'significant%20improvements%20to%20enhance%20passenger%20safety'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENDTV%C2%A0Ground%20Report%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-delhi-railway-station-stampede-ndtv-ground-report-12-hours-after-incident-ndls-remains-crowded-7722433%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20Delhi%20Rail%20Station%20Still%20Crowded%20Day%20After%20Stampede%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20measures%20will%20include%20special%20'holding%20areas'%20-%20with%20colour-coded%20sections%20and%20pathways%20for%20crowd%20movement%20-%20for%2060%20stations%20that%20usually%20see%20overcrowding%20due%20to%20the%20Maha%20Kumbh%20rush.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%2060%20will%20be%20designated%20as%20'high-traffic'%20railway%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20these%2060%2C%20crowds%20at%2035%20stations%20connecting%20directly%20to%20Prayagraj%20will%20be%20monitored%20on%20a%20real-time%20basis%20by%20a%20centralised%20'war%20room'.%20This%20is%20critical%20since%2090%20per%20cent%20of%20Kumbh%20devotees%20(the%20overall%20number%20swells%20in%20a%20Maha%20Kumbh%20year%20such%20as%20this)%20come%20from%20four%20states%20within%20300km%20of%20Prayagraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20passenger%20traffic%20at%20a%20single%20station%20on%20%3Cem%3E'%3C%2Fem%3Em%3Cem%3Eauni%20amavasya%3C%2Fem%3E'%20(i.e.%2C%20January%2029%2C%20when%20a%20stampede%20at%20the%20'%3Cem%3Esangam%3C%2Fem%3E'%20in%20Prayagraj%20killed%2030%20people)%2C%20was%20a%20staggering%2017%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVIDEO%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fvideo%2Fmoments-that-led-to-maha-kumbh-stampede-caught-on-cam-895213%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMoments%20That%20Led%20To%20Maha%20Kumbh%20Stampede%20Caught%20On%20Cam%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%2035%20stations%2C%20which%20include%20those%20in%20Delhi%2C%20will%20be%20specially%20monitored%2C%20officials%20said.%20As%20part%20of%20that%20'special%20monitoring'%2C%20Delhi's%20railway%20stations%20will%20see%20over%20200%20new%20CCTV%20cameras%20set%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20law%20enforcement%20perspective%2C%20Delhi%20Police%20has%20deployed%20six%20Inspector-rank%20officers%20to%20oversee%20crowd%20management%20at%20NDLS.%20According%20to%20news%20agency%20IANS%2C%20these%20officers%20have%20been%20handpicked%20for%20experience%20in%20handling%20ops%20at%20NDLS%2C%20one%20of%20India's%20busiest%20transit%20hubs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20there%20has%20been%20increased%20deployment%20of%20the%20Railway%20Police%20Force.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20railway%20officials%20said%20they%20had%2C%20with%20immediate%20effect%2C%20also%20stopped%20the%20sale%20of%20platform%20tickets%20for%20seven%20hours%20starting%20from%204%20pm%3B%20these%20normally%20allow%20non-passengers%20into%20the%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%2C%20however%2C%20will%20not%20apply%20to%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20or%20senior%20citizens%2C%20Himanshu%20Shekhar%20Upadhyay%2C%20the%20Chief%20Public%20Relations%20Officer%20of%20Northern%20Railways%2C%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Led%20To%20Stampede%20At%20Delhi%20Station%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEyewitnesses%20claimed%20the%20stampede%20broke%20out%20after%20a%20rumour%20spread%20that%20the%20Prayagraj%20Express%20was%20going%20to%20arrive%20on%20a%20different%20platform.%20Railway%20authorities%2C%20however%2C%20have%20denied%20the%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%7C%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdid-platform-change-announcement-lead-to-delhi-stampede-what-cops-say-7723155%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDid%20Platform%20Change%20Lead%20To%20Delhi%20Stampede%3F%20What%20Cops%20Say%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Upadhyay%20said%20some%20people%20coming%20down%20from%20a%20footbridge%20connecting%20platform%2014%20and%2015%20slipped%20and%20fell%20on%20others.%20%26quot%3BNo%20train%20was%20cancelled%2C%20nor%20was%20there%20any%20change%20in%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20said%C2%A0%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20incident%2C%20the%20Patna-bound%20Magadh%20Express%20was%20at%20platform%2014%20and%20the%20New%20Delhi-Jammu%20Uttar%20Sampark%20Kranti%20Express%20was%20at%20platform%2015.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20input%20from%20agencies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENDTV%20is%20now%20available%20on%20WhatsApp%20channels.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whatsapp.com%2Fchannel%2F0029Va4lixw7z4kcvZI9JM12%5C%22%3EClick%20on%20the%20link%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20all%20the%20latest%20updates%20from%20NDTV%20on%20your%20chat.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739782740000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F7jcaa93o_new-delhi-railway-station-stampede_625x300_16_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnew-delhi-railway-station-stampede-colour-codes-war-rooms-crowd-control-overhaul-after-delhi-station-s