3EIf%20a%20FASTag%20remains%20blacklisted%20for%2010%20minutes%20after%20being%20scanned%2C%20the%20payment%20will%20also%20be%20rejected.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20both%20conditions%20are%20met%2C%20the%20system%20will%20decline%20the%20transaction%20with%20error%20code%20176%2C%20and%20the%20vehicle%20will%20be%20charged%20double%20the%20toll%20fee%20as%20a%20penalty.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrace%20Period%20for%20Recharging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EUsers%20now%20have%20a%2070-minute%20window%20before%20reaching%20the%20toll%20booth%20to%20rectify%20their%20FASTag%20status.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIf%20a%20FASTag%20is%20recharged%20within%2010%20minutes%20of%20an%20attempted%20transaction%2C%20users%20may%20qualify%20for%20a%20penalty%20refund%20and%20only%20pay%20the%20standard%20toll%20fee.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDelayed%20Transactions%20-%20Additional%20Charges%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnIf%20a%20toll%20transaction%20is%20processed%20more%20than%2015%20minutes%20after%20passing%20the%20toll%20reader%2C%20users%20may%20face%20extra%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChargebacks%20-%20Cooling%20Period%20Introduced%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnBanks%20can%20raise%20chargeback%20requests%20for%20incorrect%20deductions%20due%20to%20blacklisted%20or%20low-balance%20FASTags%20only%20after%20a%2015-day%20cooling%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20These%20Rules%20Mean%20for%20FASTag%20Users%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ENo%20last-minute%20recharges%20-%20If%20a%20FASTag%20has%20been%20blacklisted%20for%20more%20than%2060%20minutes%20before%20reaching%20a%20toll%2C%20a%20recharge%20won't%20help%20at%20the%20last%20moment.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EPenalty%20refund%20possible%20-%20If%20a%20recharge%20is%20done%20within%2010%20minutes%20of%20scanning%2C%20users%20can%20request%20a%20refund%20and%20avoid%20paying%20double%20toll%20charges.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStrict%20t