mid%20a%20crackdown%20by%20the%20Donald%20Trump%20administration%20against%20illegal%20immigrants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20deportees'%20arrived%20within%2024%20hours%20of%20a%20US%20military%20aircraft%20bringing%20back%20a%20batch%20of%20116%20Indians%20living%20illegally%20in%20that%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20a%20legal%20entry%20as%20promised%2C%20Mandeep's%20travel%20agent%20put%20him%20on%20the%20'donkey%20route'%20%E2%80%93%20an%20illegal%20and%20risky%20pathway%20used%20by%20migrants%20to%20enter%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20in%20Amritsar%2C%20Mandeep%20(38)%20showed%20several%20videos%20of%20the%20perilous%20journey%20his%20travel%20agent%20and%20sub-agents%20put%20him%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20spoke%20to%20my%20agent%2C%20he%20said%20within%20one%20month%20I%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20the%20US%20in%20a%20legal%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20Mandeep%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agent%20demanded%20Rs%2040%20lakh%2C%20which%20he%20paid%20in%20two%20instalments.%20The%20journey%20began%20from%20Amritsar%20to%20Delhi%20last%20August%20on%20a%20flight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20Delhi%2C%20I%20was%20taken%20to%20Mumbai%2C%20then%20Nairobi%2C%20and%20onwards%20to%20Amsterdam%20through%20another%20nation.%20From%20there%2C%20we%20were%20taken%20to%20Suriname.%20When%20I%20reached%20there%2C%20the%20sub-agents%20demanded%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20which%20was%20paid%20back%20home%20by%20my%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDetailing%20the%20uncertain%20journey%20that%20began%20from%20there%2C%20Mandeep%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BFrom%20Suriname%2C%20we%20boarded%20a%20vehicle%20which%20was%20cramped%20with%20many%20people%20like%20me.%20We%20were%20taken%20to%20Guyana.%20From%20there%20it%20was%20non-stop%20travel%20for%20days.%20We%20crossed%20Guyana%2C%20then%20Bolivia%20before%20reaching%20Ecuador.%26quot%3B%20The%20group%20was%20then%20made%20to%20cross%20the%20Panama%20jungles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHere%20we%20were%20told%20by%20fellow%20travellers%20that%20if%20we%20ask%20too%20many%20questions%2C%20we%20could%20be%20shot.%20For%2013%20days%2C%20we%20moved%20through%20the%20treacherous%20route%20that%20included%2012%20canals.%20Crocodiles%2C%20snakes%20%E2%80%93%20we%20had%20to%20bear%20all.%20Some%20were%20given%20sticks%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20dangerous%20reptiles%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20ate%20half-baked%20'rotis'%20and%20sometimes%20noodles%2C%20as%20proper%20food%20was%20a%20distant%20thing.%20We%20used%20to%20travel%2012%20hours%20a%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mandeep%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20made%20a%20halt%20at%20Costa%20Rica%20after%20crossing%20Panama%2C%20and%20then%20began%20their%20journey%20to%20Honduras%2C%20where%2C%20Mandeep%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20got%20to%20finally%20eat%20some%20rice.%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%9CBut%20we%20did%20not%20get%20to%20eat%20anything%20while%20crossing%20through%20Nicaragua.%20In%20Guatemala%2C%20however%2C%20we%20were%20lucky%20to%20get%20some%20curd%20rice%20to%20eat.%20By%20the%20time%20we%20reached%20Tijuana%2C%20my%20beard%20was%20trimmed%20forcibly%2C%E2%80%9D%20Mandeep%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20January%2027%2C%20they%20were%20arrested%20by%20the%20Border%20Police%20after%20they%20were%20made%20to%20cross%20the%20border%20to%20sneak%20into%20the%20US%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20authorities%20told%20us%20that%20we%20will%20be%20deported.%20We%20were%20put%20in%20a%20detention%20centre%20for%20some%20days%20before%20we%20were%20sent%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20February%205%2C%20the%20first%20US%20military%20aircraft%20carrying%20104%20illegal%20Indian%20immigrants%20landed%20at%20the%20Amritsar%20airport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20publishe