0with%20them.%20Suddenly%2C%20if%20things%20go%20wrong%2C%20the%20same%20people%20vanish.%20So%20it%20is%20very%20important%20to%20know%20who%20your%20true%20friends%20are%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERahane%20dug%20deep%20in%20his%20memory%20as%20he%20recalled%20those%20times%20when%20he%20had%20started%20to%20gain%20attention%20on%20the%20international%20circuit.%20The%20batter%20revealed%20that%20he%20only%20bought%20a%20second-hand%20WagonR%20when%20he%20made%20his%20India%20debut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20where%20my%20family%20values%20came%20in.%20They%20never%20said%20don't%20spend%2C%20but%20they%20only%20said%20if%20it's%20needed%2C%20do%20it.%20I%20bought%20a%20car%20very%20late%20in%20my%20life%2C%20I%20used%20to%20take%20a%20lift%20from%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Nilesh%20Kulkarni%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F264-nilesh-kulkarni-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENilesh%20Kulkarni%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Avishkar%20Salvi%20or%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pravin%20Tambe%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1721-pravin-tambe-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPravin%20Tambe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20bought%20a%20second-hand%20WagonR%20when%20I%20played%20for%20India.%20People%20said%20bada%20car%20le%20but%20for%20me%20it%20was%20about%20travelling%20in%20comfort.%20I%20wanted%20to%20invest%20wisely.%20After%20two%20years%2C%20I%20bought%20a%20Honda%20City%2C%26quot%3B%20Rahane%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739777100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fp19rnbio_rahane-ranji-twitter_625x300_10_March_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fbought-second-hand-wagonr-when-i-played-for-india-ajinkya-rahane-opens-up-on-familys-struggles-7728938%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ajinkya%20Rahane%20opened%20up%20never-seen-before%20chapter%20of%20his%20life%20as%20he%20dug%20deep%20into%20the%20financial%20struggles%20his%20family%20went%20th