3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fu%3E%20on%20how%20the%20IRI%20had%20been%20funded%20by%20the%20USAID%20to%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3Edestabilize%20Bangladesh%20politics.%3C%2Fi%3E%E2%80%9D%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20question%20-%20%C2%A0was%20the%20%2421%20million%20funding%20canceled%20by%20DOGE%20was%20for%20regime%20change%20operations%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20India%20Trail%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20from%20the%20IFES%20and%20the%20NDI%20that%20a%20large%20portion%20of%20the%20funding%20for%20India%20appears%20to%20have%20come.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20website%20of%20the%20NGO%20shows%20that%20it%20partners%20with%20another%20NGO%20-%20Asian%20Network%20for%20Free%20Elections%20(ANFREL)%20which%20actively%20works%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDTV%20perused%20the%20financial%20statements%20and%20annual%20reports%20of%20the%20IFES%20and%20found%20multiple%20transfers%20for%20projects%20in%20India.%20However%2C%20the%20details%20of%20these%20projects%20are%20not%20immediately%20clear.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20picked%20up%20an%20MOU%20signed%20between%20IFES%20and%20the%20ECI%20and%20alleged%20that%20then%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20SY%20Quraishi%20is%20involved%20with%20this%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOnce%20again%2C%20it%20is%20George%20Soros%2C%20a%20known%20associate%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%20and%20the%20Gandhis%2C%20whose%20shadow%20looms%20over%20our%20electoral%20process.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnIn%202012%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20S.Y.%20Quraishi%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20signed%20an%20MoU%20with%20The%20International%20Foundation%20for%20Electoral...%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPO13Iyroee%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FPO13Iyroee%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FgdgAQoDbPh%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FgdgAQoDbPh%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Amit%20Malviya%20(%40amitmalviya)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Famitmalviya%2Fstatus%2F1890989529781215669%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2016%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuraishi%2C%20however%2C%20provided%20a%20response%20to%20PTI%20which%20is%20reproduced%20here%20in%20full%20-%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%26quot%3BThe%20report%20in%20a%20section%20of%20Media%20about%20an%20MoU%20by%20ECI%20in%202012%20when%20I%20was%20CEC%2C%20for%20funding%20of%20certain%20million%20dollars%20by%20a%20US%20agency%20for%20raising%20voter%20turnout%20in%20India%20does%20not%20have%20an%20iota%20of%20fact.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EYes%2C%20there%20was%20a%20MOU%20with%20IFES%20in%202012%20when%20I%20was%20CEC%20like%20we%20had%20with%20many%20other%20agencies%20and%20Election%20Management%20Bodies%20to%20facilitate%20training%20for%20desirous%20countries%20at%20ECI%20's%20training%20and%20resource%20centre%2C%20IIIDEM%2C%20which%20was%20very%20new%20at%20that%20stage.%20There%20was%20no%20financing%20or%20even%20promise%20of%20finance%20involved%20in%20MoU%2C%20forget%20X%20or%20Y%20amount.%20The%20MoU%20in%20fact%20made%20it%20clear%20in%20black%20and%20white%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20financial%20and%20legal%20obligation%20of%20any%20kind%20on%20either%20side.%20%C2%A0This%20stipulation%20was%20made%20at%20two%20different%20places%20to%20leave%20no%20scope%20for%20any%20ambiguity.%20Any%20mention%20of%20any%20funds%20in%20connection%20with%20this%20MoU%20is%20completely%20false%20and%20malicious%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Quraishi's%20statement.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENDI%20has%20on%20its%20website%2C%20a%20distorted%20map%20of%20India%20which%20shows%20Kashmir%20as%20not%20being%20part%20of%20India.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20has%20on%20its%20%3Cu%3E%3Ca%20