%20company's%20post%20on%20Saturday%20also%20indicated%20that%20the%20drones%20used%20in%20the%20attack%20weren't%20officially%20supplied%20but%20received%20through%20civilian%20donations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20sponsor%20of%20the%20defeat%20is%20the%20Sternenko%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20unit%20wrote%20on%20its%20social%20media%20channel%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Ukrainian%20crowdfunding%20activist%20Serhii%20Sternenko.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESternenko%2C%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20drone%20crowdfunders%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20acknowledged%20the%20attacks%20on%20Saturday%2C%20calling%20the%20drone%20unit%20%26quot%3Btrue%20masters%20of%20their%20craft%26quot%3B%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fssternenko%2F40052%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%20on%20his%20Telegram%20channel.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20provide%20them%20with%20drones%20upon%20individual%20requests%20specifically%20for%20performing%20such%20tasks%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20air%20defense%20systems%20were%20positioned%20at%20the%20Russian%20rear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrone%20warfare%20continues%20to%20evolve%20on%20the%20battlefield%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20with%20loitering%20munitions%20becoming%20so%20ubiquitous%2C%20the%20war%20fronts%20have%20increasingly%20been%20reported%20to%20become%20saturated%20with%20jammers.%20That%20prompted%20Russian%20units%20to%20bring%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-unjammable-fiber-optic-drone-keep-pace-russia-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efiber-optic%20drones%20to%20the%20fight%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Ukrainian%20companies%20and%20brigades%20have%20been%20following%20suit%20in%20manufacturing%20their%20own%20versions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20defense%20ministry%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20sent%20by%20BI%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20or