d%20need%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fcamping-gear-cleaning-and-care%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eincluding%20a%20sleeping%20bag%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Since%20I%20didn't%20have%20one%2C%20we%20bought%20one%20ready.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20so%20excited.%20I'd%20only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshare-bed-sleepovers-cosleeping-friendship-intimacy-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eheard%20about%20sleepovers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20seen%20them%20on%20TV%2C%20and%20they%20looked%20really%20fun.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBefore%20I%20went%2C%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-daughter-long-distance-living-abroad-closer-relationship-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Emom%20told%20me%20I%20could%20call%20her%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20if%20I%20didn't%20feel%20safe%20or%20just%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20at%20the%20sleepover%20anymore.%20She'd%20be%20there%20right%20away%20to%20pick%20me%20up.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228b519ac2-9f0b-47ca-bebb-298c0202c994%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20called%20her%2C%20and%20she%20came%20as%20promised%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%2C%20I%20knew%20most%20of%20the%20girls%20there%2C%20besides%20a%20few%20of%20the%20girl's%20family%20members.%20The%20mother%20ordered%20pizza%2C%20which%20was%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20a%20good%20time.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20the%20pizza%2C%20we%20went%20upstairs%2C%20and%20as%20I%20got%20to%20the%20top%2C%20the%20birthday%20girl's%20cousin%20pushed%20me%20into%20the%20wall.%20Then%2C%20she%20started%20talking%20about%20how%20my%20braids%20were%20ugly%2C%20asking%20me%20why%20I%20had%20them%20in%20my%20hair.%20Everyone%20else%20started%20following%20the%20cousin's%20lead%20in%20making%20fun%20of%20my%20hair.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20and%20daughter%20posing%20for%20photo%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ae1457eb4be2fff9a4895d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELaVina%20Hawkins%20has%20called%20her%20mom%20multiple%20times%20throughout%20her%20life%20when%20she%20needed%20help.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20LaVina%20Hawkins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20didn't%20fight%20back%20but%20I%20did%20run%20downstairs%20and%20told%20the%20mother.%20She%20called%20all%20the%20girls%20downstairs%20and%20tried%20to%20handle%20it%2C%20but%20when%20I%20returned%20upstairs%2C%20it%20was%20radio%20silence.%20No%20one%20would%20speak%20to%20me.%20I'd%20become%20an%20outsider.%20It%20felt%20awful%20to%20be%20excluded%20after%20having%20been%20invited.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20I%20could%20think%20to%20do%20was%20phone%20my%20mom.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20went%20downstairs%20and%20used%20the%20home%20phone%20to%20call%20her.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BMom%2C%20come%20get%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20on%20my%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20replied.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20didn't%20ask%20what%20happened%20%E2%80%94%20she%20just%20said%20she%20was%20coming.%20I%20felt%20so%20safe.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMinutes%20later%2C%20she%20knocked%20on%20the%20door%2C%20and%20I%20got%20my%20things%20and%20left%20with%20her.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20we%20were%20in%20the%20car%2C%20she%20asked%20what%20happened.%20She%20told%20me%20sometimes%20people%20are%20afraid%20of%20what%20they%20don't%20know.%20She%20said%20everything%20was%20OK%20%E2%80%94%20that%20I%20was%20safe.%20We%20went%20out%20for%20ice%20cream%20and%20then%20watched%20movies%20together.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22558e3190-fed4-4521-84c8-47e4f50f3315%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20reminded%20me%20that%20she%20would%20always%20show%20up%20for%20me%20when%20needed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThroughout%20our%20childhood%2C%20my%20mom%20kept%20saying%20the%20same%20thing%20to%20myself%20and%20my%20siblings%20%E2%80%94%20that%20she%20would%20come%20to%20pick%20us%20up%20if%20ever%20we%20felt%20unsafe%20and%20needed%20her.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20remember%20when%20I%20was%20in%20high%20school%2C%20I%20had%20been%20out%20with%20friends%20of%20friends%20and%20everyone%20had%20been%20drinking.%20One%20person%20said%20they%20would%20drive%20us.%20I%20said%20I%20would%20call%20my%20mom%20to%20come%20get%20me.%20The%20friend%20I%20was%20with%20didn't%20want%20me%20to%2C%20but%20I%20told%20her%20that%20it%20didn't%20matter%20where%20we%20were%20or%20what%20we%20were%20doing%3B%20my%20mom%20would%20come%20get%20us%20without%20asking%20a%20single%20question.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMom%20came%20and%20got%20me.%20The%20friends%20whose%20car%20I%20refused%20to%20get%20in%20ended%20up%20getting%20in%20a%20car%20accident%20that%20night.%20The%20driver%20died.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYears%20later%2C%20when%20my%20second%20child%20was%20just%20a%20few%20months%20old%2C%20I%20was%20struggling%20with%20postpartum%20depression.%20I%20woke%20up%20one%20morning%20and%20felt%20awful%2C%20like%20checking%20out.%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20feed%20my%20child.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20I%20wasn't%20ashamed%20to%20call%20my%20mom.%20She%20wouldn't%20judge%20me.%20She%20would%20just%20come.%20%26quot%3BMom%2C%20come%20get%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20told%20her%20over%20the%20phone.%20She%20knew%20from%20my%20voice%20something%20was%20off.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20on%20the%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20She%20kept%20me%20on%20the%20